OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1775214171
OL,3,CStage removed from Jim Clark Rally
OL,4,Cfollowing co-drivers death
OL,6,FChanges have been made to this year's
OL,7,FJim Clark Rally as a 'mark of respect'
OL,8,Fto Dai Roberts who died in a crash
OL,9,Fduring last year's competition.
OL,11,FThe 39-year-old co-driver from
OL,12,FCarmarthen in South Wales was
OL,13,Fpronounced dead at the scene,
OL,14,Ffollowing a crash on the Edrom Mains
OL,15,Froad, just outside Duns, on Saturday
OL,16,F24 May 2025.
OL,18,FDai had enjoyed a career spanning 22
OL,19,Fyears and at the time of his death,
OL,20,Ftributes to his character, talent and
OL,21,Flove for motorsport poured in.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/6
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
