CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1775214171
OL,3,CStage removed from Jim Clark Rally
OL,4,Cfollowing co-drivers death
OL,6,FThe driver in the car with him, 27-
OL,7,Fyear-old James Williams, was taken to
OL,8,Fthe Royal Infirmary of Edinburgh
OL,9,Fhospital where he was treated for
OL,10,Fserious injuries.
OL,12,FThe annual rally is set to go ahead
OL,13,Fagain this year from 22-24 May in
OL,14,FDuns, but it will no longer run the
OL,15,FEdrom stage.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/6
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
