CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1775214171
OL,3,CStage removed from Jim Clark Rally
OL,4,Cfollowing co-drivers death
OL,6,FA spokesperson for the Jim Clark Rally
OL,7,Fsaid: "The Jim Clark Rally will not
OL,8,Frun the 'Edrom' stage in 2026 as a
OL,9,Fmark of respect for the tragic death
OL,10,Fof co-driver Dai Roberts last year on
OL,11,Fthe stage.
OL,13,F"A new test in the region will run in
OL,14,Fits place, named 'Manderston'. The
OL,15,Fdecision not to route any stage past
OL,16,Fthe location of the accident was taken
OL,17,Fvery early in the planning of the 2026
OL,18,Froute; Dai's memory is still very much
OL,19,Fin the thoughts of the organisers."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/6
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
