OL,3,CStage removed from Jim Clark Rally
OL,4,Cfollowing co-drivers death
OL,6,FFirst held in 1970, the rally is a
OL,7,Fclosed road event which takes place in
OL,8,Fthe Duns area of the Scottish Borders
OL,9,Fevery year.
OL,11,FIt is named after two time Formula One
OL,12,Fchampion, motorsport legend, and
OL,13,FBerwickshire farmer Jim Clark.
OL,15,FThe rally is a prominent round of the
OL,16,FBritish Rally Championship (BRC), the
OL,17,FProtyre National Asphalt Rally
OL,18,FChampionship, and the Scottish Rally
OL,19,FChampionship.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/6
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
