OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1775214171
OL,3,CStage removed from Jim Clark Rally
OL,4,Cfollowing co-drivers death
OL,6,FIn 2014, three spectators were killed
OL,7,Fand six more were injured at the event
OL,8,Fwhen two cars lost control and veered
OL,9,Finto viewing areas.
OL,11,FA fatal accident inquiry later found
OL,12,Fthe deaths could have been prevented
OL,13,Fif people had been clearly banned from
OL,14,Fstanding in the area where the crash
OL,15,Fhappened.
OL,17,FThe event returned five years later in
OL,18,F2019, after "rigorous steps" were
OL,19,Ftaken to ensure safety.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/6
